headline: General Dynamics (GD): Valuation Check After Double-Digit Earnings Growth and Record Defense Backlog
summary: General Dynamics (GD) just strung together several quarters of double digit earnings growth, backed by a record backlog and fresh U.S. Navy contracts, putting the stock squarely in focus for defense oriented investors. headline: The Bull Case For General Dynamics (GD) Could Change Following New Navy Deal And Wage-Fixing Lawsuit
summary: In recent months, General Dynamics has reported three consecutive quarters of double-digit earnings growth, secured a US$1.70 billion U.S. Navy fleet replenishment oiler contract, expanded its AI-focused GDIT partnership with Google Public Sector, and attracted fresh analyst coverage from BNP Paribas Exane.
